OL,3,CFormer firefighters demand pensions
OL,4,Cfor service
OL,6,FTwo former part-time firefighters are
OL,7,Fcalling on authorities to pay them a
OL,8,Fpension in recognition of their
OL,9,Fservice.
OL,11,FBob Duncan and Bill Thompson each
OL,12,Fspent more than a decade working as on-
OL,13,Fcall - or 'retained' - firefighters in
OL,14,Fin , on top of doing full time jobs
OL,15,Felsewhere.
