OL,3,CFormer firefighters demand pensions
OL,4,Cfor service
OL,6,FBut they both left their roles before
OL,7,Fthe date at which pensions were
OL,8,Fintroduced for part-time crew members,
OL,9,Fwhich they say is short-changing
OL,10,Fhundreds, possibly thousands, of
OL,11,Fpeople.
OL,13,FBoth men were among the first on the
OL,14,Fscene of an infamous fire that ripped
OL,15,Fthrough a night-time venue, called
OL,16,FPepper's, in Cleethorpes in May 1982.
OL,18,FIt was one of thousands of incidents
OL,19,Fthey attended, all while working full-
OL,20,Ftime in neighbouring factories.
