OL,6,F"By the time we got in there the roof
OL,7,Fhad gone asbestos roof you could see
OL,8,Fdaylight. There was fires all over the
OL,9,Fplace," said Mr Duncan.
OL,11,FThe pair also witnessed things that
OL,12,Fmost people never have to.
OL,14,FDescribing an incident he attended, Mr
OL,15,FDuncan said he tried to save one woman.
OL,17,F"We had to pick her up and take her
OL,18,Fout and we just laid her in the front
OL,19,Fgarden, and she died," he said.
