OL,6,F"When you get home and you've time to
OL,7,Fthink, it may not show on you but I
OL,8,Fthink it does affect you in the long
OL,9,Frun," added Mr Thompson.
OL,11,F"All firemen should be due a pension
OL,12,Ffor the service they put in," he said.
OL,14,F"They're doing the same job as the
OL,15,Fwhole time firemen so why shouldn't
OL,16,Fthey be given a pension."
