OL,6,FIt was not until 2006 that on-call
OL,7,Ffirefighters were awarded pension
OL,8,Frights like their full-time
OL,9,Fcounterparts, and more recently a
OL,10,Flegal challenge in 2018 gave pension
OL,11,Faccess to those who were working
OL,12,Fbefore 1992 - but only if they were
OL,13,Fstill firefighters by the early 2000s.
OL,15,FBoth men feel they have missed out
OL,16,Funfairly.
