OL,6,F"I think it's wrong," said Mr
OL,7,FThompson. "There's not a lot of jobs
OL,8,Fwhere you put your life on the line
OL,9,Fand a fireman's job you do put a life
OL,10,Fon the line, and I think it justifies
OL,11,Fa pension.
OL,13,FHumberside Fire and Rescue Service
OL,14,Fsaid it "values the contribution" made
OL,15,Fby on-call firefighters who help keep
OL,16,Fcommunities across the region safe.
