OL,6,FBut it added that firefighter pensions
OL,7,Fare statutory public service schemes,
OL,8,Fand that it had to apply the
OL,9,Fregulations laid down by the
OL,10,Fgovernment.
OL,12,FThe Home Office spokesperson said: "We
OL,13,Frecognise the bravery of on-call
OL,14,Ffirefighters who work tirelessly to
OL,15,Fprotect our communities."
OL,17,FHowever, they also said they do not
OL,18,Fcomment on individual cases or "legal
OL,19,Fproceedings."
